76561198023300019,Recommended,266510,14710376,"Posted: 1 March, 2015",all,Lotherien,"I like fantasy, I'm an huge fan of Dragon Age and Neverwinter Knights series, I love DnD.This game is the proof that you don't need stunning graphics or an epic story to create a wonderful product. The game system is brilliant, the dialogs are very nice and the overal gaming experience is superbe.You play as an unknown traveler, who meets a wizard which conducts a game of fate using cards. Each game has a ""final boss"" and you must ""travel"" into a path made by cards. Each card you reveal may be a combat encounter, a merchant, a mistery, and so on... Once you reveal the card with the boss you acquire new cards and another game is unlocked with a new boss.I found the combat system very intuitive (somewhat similar to Batman Arkham) and easy to use with a controller."
