,Recommended,266510,29172733,Posted: 10 January,all,AngryCrusader,"This game is a hidden gem. One of the most unique games I got a hold of. Remember when you used to play Yu-Gi-Oh back in the day and you imagined the characters and monsters on the cards fought each other? This game does exactly that. You're playing a card game of life and death with a mysterious man that calls himself ''The Dealer''. You're an adventurer, and the cards you draw shape your adventure and ultimately your fate. The game mostly consists of dialogue choices, but there are also combat events. And boy, aren't those fun. The combat is basically the same as the Batman Arkham series, so yeah it is pretty badass and fluid. Definitely deserves it's full price tag, a steal on sale."
